{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-tangfeng-005__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-tangfeng-005", "source_id": "guofeng-tangfeng-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·唐風·005.1", "text_original": "綢繆束薪，三星在天。今夕何夕？見此良人！子兮子兮！如此良人何！", "text_normalized": "綢繆束薪，三星在天。今夕何夕？見此良人！子兮子兮！如此良人何！", "notes": "綢繆 Chinese stanza 1."}
